About the show (From the website)
How do you describe the offbeat antics of David Feherty? The New York Times called him a cross between Oprah Winfrey and Johnny Carson. His irreverent humor and undeniable charm proves disarming for guests, and leads to a great conversation, and a whole lot of laughs.
